snippet.textDisplay: In 2003 at the TIME of SARS OUTBREAK, There was NO SOCIAL MEDIA, SMARTPHONE (LIKE Android, Twitter, Facebook, Youtube, MySpace, WeChat, Weibo, Gmail), NO Netflix. There were Flip-Phones, Nintendo GameCube, XBOX, PS2, Game Boy Advance
